QuestData.Title: A Little Wetwork
QuestData.Description: The shattered remnants of the Iron Horde pour into Tanaan through Ironhold Harbor. If we knew more about their fleet we could dispatch countermeasures from your shipyard in Shadowmoon.$b$bPerhaps you could gather some naval intelligence for our cause?
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $oa Iron Horde Naval Manifests from forces in Ironhold Harbor.
